      "items": [
        {
          "type": 1,
          "content": {
            "json": "## Análise de Uso — Métricas do Azure Monitor\n\nSelecione uma **VNET** para ver a comparação de métricas dos Storage Accounts associados.\n\n> 💡 **Navegação**: Com 5.000+ contas, a filtragem por VNET reduz o escopo para um número gerenciável (tipicamente 10-200 por VNET). Use o filtro na grid para refinar ainda mais.\n>\n> **Transactions** = 0 por 30+ dias → candidata à remoção. **UsedCapacity** > 0 com Transactions = 0 → dados armazenados sem acesso ativo (verificar migração).\n>\n> A grid de **Comparação de Métricas** mostra Transações, Capacidade, Ingress e Egress para todas as contas na VNET selecionada. Na grid de **Inventário** abaixo, clique em uma conta para ver os gráficos detalhados."
          },
          "name": "UsageDescription"
        },
        {
          "type": 9,
          "content": {
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "parameters": [
              {
                "id": "c1d2e3f4-0002-0002-0002-000000000001",
                "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                "name": "UsageVNET",
                "label": "VNET",
                "type": 2,
                "isRequired": true,
                "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tolower(tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId))\r\n| where targetResourceId contains 'microsoft.storage/storageaccounts'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| extend vnetId = tolower(strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourcegroups/', peRG, '/providers/microsoft.network/virtualnetworks/', vnetName))\r\n| summarize StorageAccounts = dcount(targetResourceId), PEs = count() by vnetId, vnetName\r\n| project value = vnetId, label = strcat(vnetName, ' (', StorageAccounts, ' contas, ', PEs, ' PEs)'), selected = false\r\n| order by label asc",
                "crossComponentResources": [
                  "{Subscriptions}"
                ],
                "queryType": 1,
                "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
                "value": "/subscriptions/941a3b59-bb72-46d2-9a88-00b3e139eb25/resourcegroups/rgdvtranscvnet/providers/microsoft.network/virtualnetworks/vnetdvtranscbrazilsouth"
              }
            ],
            "style": "pills",
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          "name": "UsageVNETSelector"
        },
        {
          "type": 9,
          "content": {
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "parameters": [
              {
                "id": "c1d2e3f4-0002-0002-0002-000000000002",
                "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                "name": "UsageStorageIds",
                "type": 2,
                "multiSelect": true,
                "quote": "",
                "delimiter": ",",
                "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tolower(tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId))\r\n| where targetResourceId contains 'microsoft.storage/storageaccounts'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| extend vnetId = tolower(strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourcegroups/', peRG, '/providers/microsoft.network/virtualnetworks/', vnetName))\r\n| where vnetId == '{UsageVNET}'\r\n| distinct targetResourceId\r\n| project value = targetResourceId, label = targetResourceId, selected = true",
                "crossComponentResources": [
                  "{Subscriptions}"
                ],
                "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
                "typeSettings": {
                  "additionalResourceOptions": [
                    "value::all"
                  ],
                  "showDefault": false
                },
                "defaultValue": "value::all",
                "queryType": 1,
                "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
              }
            ],
            "style": "pills",
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          "conditionalVisibility": {
            "parameterName": "UsageVNET",
            "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
            "value": ""
          },
          "name": "UsageStorageIdsParam"
        },
